mondrian.olap

Class Formula

  • java.lang.Object
    • mondrian.olap.QueryPart
      • mondrian.olap.Formula
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Walkable

    public class Formula
extends QueryPart
    A Formula is a clause in an MDX query which defines a Set or a Member.
